




{"id":4495,"date":"2020-11-09T16:03:54","date_gmt":"2020-11-09T09:03:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=4495"},"modified":"2022-06-28T13:22:59","modified_gmt":"2022-06-28T06:22:59","slug":"ban-tuong-tac-nhom-thong-minh-ifun","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/ban-tuong-tac-nhom-thong-minh-ifun\/","title":{"rendered":"B\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m Inno iFUN, gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap tr\u1ebb v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 v\u1eeba h\u1ecdc."},"content":{"rendered":"<p>B\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m th\u00f4ng minh Inno iFun gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 gi\u00fap tr\u1ebb v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 v\u1eeba h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i 4.0 nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay, \u0111a ph\u1ea7n tr\u1ebb em d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u y\u00eau th\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 Smartphone, Tablet, c\u00e1c m\u00e1y game \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed,.. thay v\u00ec tham gia c\u00e1c tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u00e2n gian nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00e2y tr\u0103n tr\u1edf cho c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh v\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean t\u1ed1t hay kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi cho c\u00e1c em nh\u1ecf ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4496 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ban-tuong-tac-nhom-1.jpg\" alt=\"B\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m th\u00f4ng minh inno ifun\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng b\u00e2ng khu\u00e2ng n\u00e0y Sao Mai Education \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p b\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m th\u00f4ng minh iFUN v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap c\u00e1c em nh\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac t\u1eeb b\u00e9, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 giao ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c em. V\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n h\u1ecdc li\u1ec7u s\u1eb5n c\u00f3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c em ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng, ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ham h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4497 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ban-tuong-tac-nhom-2.jpg\" alt=\"B\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m th\u00f4ng minh - Sao Mai\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<div dir=\"auto\">V\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho c\u00e1c Tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ea7m non nh\u1eb1m \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 th\u00f4ng minh trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc. B\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho c\u00e1c em trong vi\u1ec7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m, ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc v\u1edbi nhau nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c em trao d\u1ed3i th\u00eam k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng giao ti\u1ebfp.<\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><\/div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4499 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ban-tuong-tac-nhom-4.jpg\" alt=\"B\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m ifun\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" title=\"\"><\/div>\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 80%;\">B\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>B\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m t\u00edch h\u1ee3p m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi 30 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea1m cho ph\u00e9p 4 em t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c c\u00f9ng l\u00fac b\u1eb1ng tay ho\u1eb7c b\u00fat v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn FullHD v\u1edbi k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 32\u201d m\u1ed9t k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00ed t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u00e1c b\u00e9 vui ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u00f3m<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng k\u00ednh c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng khung nh\u1ef1a theo ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n WHO \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i cho tr\u1ebb em.<\/li>\n<li>T\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m Smartclass+ c\u1ee7a <a href=\"https:\/\/robotel.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Robotel<\/a> gi\u00fap gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i, chia s\u1ebd c\u00e1c file \u0111a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng cho k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc th\u00f4ng minh trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/li>\n<li>Dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u01b0u tr\u1eef l\u1edbn 16GB Nand Flash, b\u1ecd\u0302 nh\u01a1\u0301 RAM DDR4 4GB, Ch\u1ea1y tr\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Android 7.1 ho\u1eb7c cao h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i WiFi 802.11 b\/g\/n\/ac 2.4G\/5G v\u00e0 Bluetooth 4.1<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-4498 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/ban-tuong-tac-nhom-3.jpg\" alt=\"B\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><em><strong>&gt;&gt; Xem chi ti\u1ebft th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m: <a href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/ban-tuong-tac-nhom-32-inch-inno-ifun-321\/\">(Click \u0111\u1ec3 xem)<\/a><\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c nh\u00f3m th\u00f4ng minh Inno iFun gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 gi\u00fap tr\u1ebb v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 v\u1eeba h\u1ecdc. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i 4.0 nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nay, \u0111a ph\u1ea7n tr\u1ebb em d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u y\u00eau th\u00edch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 nh\u01b0&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":9148,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4495","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4495","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4495"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4495\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9150,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4495\/revisions\/9150"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/9148"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4495"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4495"},{"taxonomy"